twarming, sometimes harrowing tour of the media that brings us together and tears us apart.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 0aDigital mediaxSocial aspects. 0aInformation technologyxSocial aspects. 0aTelevision viewers. 0aTelevisionxSocial aspects. 7aTechnology & Engineering / Electronics / Digital.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishz978311131929208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023z9783111318912oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Engineering, Computer Sciences 2023 Englishz978311131912408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Engineering, Computer Sciences 2023z9783111318165oZDB-23-DEI08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertNew York University Press Complete eBook-Package 2023z978311075163540uhttps://doi.org/10.18574/nyu/9781479820597.001.000140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781479820597423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781479820597/original  a978-3-11-075163-5  New York University Press Complete eBook-Package 2023b2023  a978-3-11-131912-4  EBOOK PACKAGE Engineering, Computer Sciences 2023 Englishb2023  a978-3-11-131929-2  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishb2023  aEBA_CL_CHCOMSGSEN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_CHCOMSGSEN  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESTMALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA12STME  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA18STMEE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DEIb2023  aZDB-23-DGGb2023